videos.description: Trayveon Williams runs through a huge hole for a big 40-yard run that would lead to a field goal.
videos.headline: Williams gashes Auburn defense

videos.description: Justin Madubuike sticks out his big paw to block Daniel Carlson's 48-yard field goal attempt.
videos.headline: Madubuike swats away Auburn field goal

videos.description: Kerryon Johnson juggles the ball but eventually catches it and walks in for the 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Johnson uses his hands for an easy Auburn TD

videos.description: Trayveon Williams gashes the Auburn defense again to put the Aggies at the 2-yard line.
videos.headline: Williams rips off 27-yard run to set up Aggies

videos.description: Keith Ford's second effort leads to an Aggies touchdown and puts his team back on top 10-7.
videos.headline: Ford's tough run gives Texas A&M lead

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham hits Darius Slayton in stride for a 53-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Stidham goes long to Slayton for big Auburn TD

videos.description: Nick Ruffin leaps to block the punt and Malik Miller recovers it in the end zone for the Auburn touchdown.
videos.headline: Tripucka's punt gets blocked, leads to Auburn TD

videos.description: Auburn head coach Gus Malzahn says the punt block gives his team momentum going into the second half.
videos.headline: Malzahn wants his offense to play better in 2nd half

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham rolls left and hits a wide open Ryan Davis for the 4-yard score.
videos.headline: Stidham finds an open Davis for Auburn TD

videos.description: Texas A&M's Shane Tripucka's low punt bounces off the head of his teammate and rolls for a 16-yard punt.
videos.headline: Tripucka punts it off his own guy

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham delivers a dime to Darius Slayton for 46 yards that would lead to an Auburn touchdown.
videos.headline: Auburn's Stidham goes deep to Slayton

videos.description: Nick Starkel hits Damion Ratley who uses his speed to do the rest for the score.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Ratley takes slant 62 yards to the house

videos.description: Armani Watts easily blocks Daniel Carlson's 52-yard field goal attempt.
videos.headline: Texas A&M blocks another field goal

videos.description: Eli Stove gets the edge and stretches inside the pylon for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Stove dives in for Auburn TD

videos.description: Trayveon Williams breaks multiple tackles on a 72-yard kickoff return.
videos.headline: Williams takes kickoff 72 yards to keep Texas A&M alive

videos.description: Nick Starkel fires a pass to Damion Ratley on a slant for a score.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Starkel hits Ratley for quick strike TD

videos.description: Auburn head coach Gus Malzahn has high praise for RB Kerryon Johnson and says he's proud of his red zone defense.
videos.headline: Malzahn: Johnson one of the best backs in the country

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham tosses three touchdown passes as No. 14 Auburn tops Texas A&M 42-27.
videos.headline: Stidham leads Auburn past Texas A&M
